title: Shutdown Fullcast 3.32
description:
Spencer declares this the best week of the college football season thus far and admires the ability of Arkansas to maintain the exact same level all year while others rise and fall. Jason channels Mike Leach to tell you how trees with lips cannot be trusted and says nice things about Syracuse. Ryan says some dumb shit about Checkers and Scott Storch.
Oh, and we also discuss USC's new coach. He's a veteran who knows how to win at all levels!
